suppressPackageStartupMessages({
    library(igraph)
    library(mclust)
    library(gmmase)
})

set.seed(123)
pm <- cbind( c(.2, .001), c(.001, .3) )
g <- sample_sbm(100, pref.matrix=pm, block.sizes=c(30,70), directed=TRUE)
summary(g)
## IGRAPH bd29a4e D--- 100 1620 -- Stochastic block-model
## + attr: name (g/c), loops (g/l)
res <- gmmase(g)
## 1. Finding an lcc...
## IGRAPH 00b454e D-W- 100 1620 -- Stochastic block-model
## + attr: name (g/c), loops (g/l), weight (e/n)
## 2. Passing-to-rank...
## IGRAPH 00b454e D-W- 100 1620 -- Stochastic block-model
## + attr: name (g/c), loops (g/l), weight (e/n)
## 3. Embedding the graph into dmax = 20...
## 4. Finding an elbow (dimension reduction)...

## , use dhat =  2 
## 5. Clustering using GMM...

## ----------------------------------------------------
## Gaussian finite mixture model fitted by EM algorithm 
## ----------------------------------------------------
## 
## Mclust VEI (diagonal, equal shape) model with 2 components:
## 
##  log.likelihood   n df      BIC      ICL
##        544.3826 100 14 1024.293 1024.293
## 
## Clustering table:
##  1  2 
## 28 72
Y <- res$class # cluster labels
